                            <comment id="67924" author="bfaccini" created="Sun, 29 Sep 2013 08:17:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I had to re-trigger auto-tests for Change #7730 patch-set #3, due to issues (particularly the sanity-quota &quot;SLOW IO for quota_usr (user): ...&quot; error related to slow zfs perfs, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2887&quot; title=&quot;sanity-quota test_12a: slow due to ZFS VMs sharing single disk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2887&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2887&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) review-zfs test suite. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67509" author="jcl" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 07:43:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;yes will do it, I will also include style/cleaning comments from John (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3976&quot; title=&quot;sanity-hsm test_9a failure: &amp;#39;hsm flags on f.sanity-hsm.9a.1 are 0x00000009 != 0x00000001&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3976&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3976&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67395" author="jay" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 17:19:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi JC, will you please include the fix for test_106(&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3983&quot; title=&quot;sanity-hsm test_106 failure:  &amp;#39;My uuid not found in agent list&amp;#39; &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3983&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3983&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) into this patch as well? To fix it, we can add $MOUNT as the parameter of get_client_uuid().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67364" author="pjones" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 15:03:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bruno&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please look after this patch?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
